               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction (fols. 3r-8v)
 - The “Synopsis of classes” (fols.
                     3r-4r)
 - Letter of Eusebius to Carpianus (fols. 4v-5r)
 - Canon Tables
                     (fols. 5v-8v) 
 II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 9ra-42v) 
 - List of the
                     “tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew: 53 titles (fols. 9ra-10vb) 
 - Bǝsrāta
                     Mātewos “Gospel of Matthew” (Mt. 1-17:4) (fols. 11ra-42vb), incomplete 
                     
 Additiones 1-5.</summary>
